Package gui.toolbars

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MainToolbar
    Extension of JToolBar, which has specialized AbstractActions which represent shortcut icons to the ones that are in MainFrame's JMenu.
    QuickSearchPanel
    Extension of JPanel which contains QuickSearchTextField, used for quick filtering Table.
    QuickSearchTextField
    Extension of the JTextField class.
    TableToolbar
    Extension of JToolBar, which has specialized AbstractActions for record manipulation and navigation in Table and QuickSearchPanel as well.
